@startuml

' ─────────────────────────────────────────────
'  学生参加考试时序图 — Black & White Style
'  南方职业学院在线考试系统
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────

!theme plain
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "monospace"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #000000
skinparam ActorBorderColor #000000
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorFontColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor #000000
skinparam SequenceBoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

title <size:16><b>学生参加考试时序图</b></size>\n<size:11>南方职业学院在线考试系统  |  查看考试 → 开始考试 → 答题 → 提交 → 查看成绩</size>

actor "学生\n(Student)" as Student
participant "ExamList.vue\n(考试列表)" as ExamList
participant "ExamTake.vue\n(答题页面)" as ExamTake
participant "ExamResults.vue\n(成绩页面)" as ExamResults
participant "API 层\n(exam.ts)" as API
participant "ExamController\n(考试控制器)" as ExamController
participant "ExamService\n(考试服务)" as ExamService
participant "ExamSessionService\n(会话服务)" as ExamSessionService
participant "PaperService\n(试卷服务)" as PaperService
participant "QuestionService\n(题目服务)" as QuestionService
participant "CourseService\n(课程服务)" as CourseService
database "MySQL\n(数据库)" as MySQL

' ═══ 阶段一: 查看考试列表 ═══
== 阶段一: 查看我的考试 ==

Student -> ExamList : 1. 进入考试列表
ExamList -> API : 2. GET /api/exams/my
API -> ExamController : 3. getMyExams()
ExamController -> ExamService : 4. getMyExams(studentId)
ExamService -> CourseService : 5. getMyCourses(studentId)\n获取学生已加入的课程
CourseService --> ExamService : 返回课程列表
ExamService -> ExamService : 6. 查询课程的已发布考试
ExamService -> ExamSessionService : 7. 批量查询考试会话\n(检查是否已参加过)
ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 返回 sessionMap
ExamService -> ExamService : 8. 设置 studentExamStatus\n(NOT_STARTED / IN_PROGRESS / SUBMITTED)
ExamService --> ExamController : 返回考试列表 (附带状态)
ExamController --> API : Result.success(exams)
API --> ExamList : 200 OK
ExamList --> Student : 展示考试列表\n及个人考试状态

' ═══ 阶段二: 开始考试 ═══
== 阶段二: 开始考试 ==

Student -> ExamList : 9. 点击「开始考试」
ExamList -> API : 10. POST /api/exams/{id}/start
API -> ExamController : 11. startExam(id)
ExamController -> ExamService : 12. startExam(examId, studentId)

ExamService -> ExamService : 13. 校验考试状态\n(PUBLISHED / STARTED)

alt 开始考试: 未加入课程
    ExamService -> CourseService : isCourseMember(courseId, studentId)
    CourseService --> ExamService : false
    ExamService --> ExamController : <color:red>BusinessException("请先加入对应课程")</color>
else 开始考试: 考试未开始
    ExamService --> ExamController : <color:red>BusinessException("考试未开始")</color>
else 开始考试: 已参加过
    ExamService -> ExamSessionService : getByExamIdAndStudentId()
    ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 已提交
    ExamService --> ExamController : <color:red>BusinessException("已参加过该考试")</color>
else 开始考试: 可以开始
    ExamService -> ExamSessionService : 14. save(session)\nstatus=IN_PROGRESS, startedAt=now
    ExamSessionService -> MySQL : 15. INSERT INTO exam_sessions\n(student_id, exam_id, status, ...)
    MySQL --> ExamSessionService : 返回结果
    ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 返回 ExamSession
    ExamService --> ExamController : 返回 ExamSession
    ExamController --> API : Result.success(session)
    API --> ExamList : 200 OK
    ExamList -> ExamTake : 16. 跳转到答题页面
end

' ═══ 阶段三: 获取题目 ═══
== 阶段三: 获取题目并答题 ==

ExamTake -> API : 17. GET /api/exams/{id}/questions
API -> ExamController : 18. getExamQuestions(id)
ExamController -> ExamService : 19. getExamQuestions(examId, studentId)
ExamService -> CourseService : 20. isCourseMember()
CourseService --> ExamService : 确认课程成员身份
ExamService -> ExamService : 21. 校验考试状态(PUBLISHED/STARTED)\n校验: startedAt < now < endedAt + 30s
ExamService -> ExamSessionService : 22. getByExamIdAndStudentId()
ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 返回 session (必须 IN_PROGRESS)
ExamService -> ExamService : 23. 校验会话超时\nnow < startedAt + duration
ExamService -> PaperService : 24. getById(paperId)
PaperService --> ExamService : 返回 Paper (含 questionIds)
ExamService -> QuestionService : 25. listByIds(questionIds)\n批量查询题目
QuestionService --> ExamService : 返回题目列表
ExamService -> ExamService : 26. QuestionForExamResponse.from()\n移除正确答案，只保留题目内容
ExamService --> ExamController : 返回题目列表 (无答案)
ExamController --> API : Result.success(questions)
API --> ExamTake : 200 OK (题目数据)
ExamTake --> Student : 展示考试题目\n倒计时开始

' ═══ 阶段四: 自动保存 ═══
== 阶段四: 自动保存答案 (定时) ==

loop 每30秒自动保存
    ExamTake -> API : 27. PUT /api/exams/{id}/auto-save
    API -> ExamController : 28. autoSaveExam(id, answers)
    ExamController -> ExamService : 29. autoSaveExam(examId, studentId, answers)
    ExamService -> ExamSessionService : 30. getByExamIdAndStudentId()
    ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 返回 session
    ExamService -> ExamService : 31. 校验:\n- 考试未结束?\n- 未超时?\n- 状态=IN_PROGRESS?
    ExamService -> ExamSessionService : 32. updateById(session)\n仅更新 answers 字段
    ExamSessionService -> MySQL : 33. UPDATE exam_sessions\nSET answers=?\nWHERE id=?
    MySQL --> ExamSessionService : 返回结果
    ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 更新成功
    ExamService --> ExamController : 保存成功
    ExamController --> API : Result.success()
    API --> ExamTake : 200 OK
    ExamTake -> ExamTake : <color:green>自动保存完成</color>
end

' ═══ 阶段五: 提交考试 ═══
== 阶段五: 提交考试 ==

Student -> ExamTake : 34. 检查答案，点击交卷
ExamTake -> API : 35. POST /api/exams/{id}/submit
API -> ExamController : 36. submitExam(id, answers)
ExamController -> ExamService : 37. submitExam(examId, studentId, answers)
ExamService -> ExamSessionService : 38. getByExamIdAndStudentId()
ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 返回 session

ExamService -> ExamService : 39. validateAnswers()\n验证答案格式/题目归属

ExamService -> QuestionService : 40. listByIds(questionIds)\n批量查询题目 (含正确答案)
QuestionService --> ExamService : 返回题目 Map

ExamService -> ExamService : 41. 自动评分客观题

group alt [评分逻辑]
    group #EEEEEE [单选题]
        ExamService -> ExamService : checkAnswer(): 忽略大小写比较
    end
    group #EEEEEE [多选题]
        ExamService -> ExamService : checkAnswer(): 排序后比较JSON数组
    end
    group #EEEEEE [判断题]
        ExamService -> ExamService : normalizeTrueFalse(): A/正确→TRUE
    end
    group #EEEEEE [填空题]
        ExamService -> ExamService : isFillBlankCorrect(): 多答案/分隔符匹配
    end
    group #EEEEEE [简答题 (主观题)]
        ExamService -> ExamService : gradingStatus=PENDING\n分数暂为null
    end
end

ExamService -> ExamSessionService : 42. updateById(session)\nstatus=SUBMITTED/GRADED\n乐观锁防并发
ExamSessionService -> MySQL : 43. UPDATE exam_sessions\nSET answers=?, score=?, status=?\nWHERE id=? AND version=?
MySQL --> ExamSessionService : 返回结果
ExamSessionService --> ExamService : 提交成功
ExamService --> ExamController : 提交成功
ExamController --> API : Result.success()
API --> ExamTake : 200 OK
ExamTake -> ExamResults : 44. 跳转到成绩页

' ═══ 阶段六: 查看成绩 ═══
== 阶段六: 查看考试结果 ==

ExamResults -> API : 45. GET /api/exams/{id}/review-questions
API -> ExamController : 46. getReviewQuestions(id)
ExamController -> ExamService : 47. checkReviewPermission()\n(ADMIN全权/TEACHER自己/STUDENT已提交)
ExamService -> PaperService : 48. getById(paperId)
PaperService --> ExamService : 返回试卷
ExamService -> QuestionService : 49. listByIds(questionIds)
QuestionService --> ExamService : 返回完整题目 (含答案+解析)
ExamService --> ExamController : 返回题目列表
ExamController --> API : Result.success(questions)
API --> ExamResults : 200 OK (含答案和解析)
ExamResults --> Student : 展示成绩与答题回顾\n客观题得分 + 主观题状态

footer 南方职业学院 © 2026  |  权限: @RequireRole(STUDENT)  |  特性: 自动保存 / 乐观锁 / 30秒宽限 / Fisher-Yates洗牌
@enduml
